{"tid":508843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣稱聖誕為耶誕，因當年政府認為「聖誕」會冒犯到至聖先師孔子，所以就改成「耶誕」","createTime":"2017-12-24T15:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T16:02:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e06bf233668bfbdc9c572485b0a2e0432cb16c5","tid":508843,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"米！聖誕、耶誕分不清？竟和「孔子」大有關係！<br />\n<br />\n今（12月24日）是平安夜，加上適逢周六日，許多人早已計畫好和家人好友度佳節！話說都是西洋的Christmas，話說都<strong></strong>是西洋的Christmas，為何台灣會有人稱「耶誕」、「聖誕」呢？其實這和台灣歷史有關！1980年代台灣實施黨禁報禁時，因為政府認為「聖誕」會冒犯到至聖先師孔子，所以就改成「耶誕」！<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20171224001625-260405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20171224001625-260405&d=HL%2FrXwgy5U97G3dfGkx76JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0e9d87d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20171224001625-260405</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"c92fd9104615a0c55e3ff0813518413fd251515b","tid":508843,"uid":55951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"先見之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耶撚誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa883dc50efe020349ae4ea4fda2b26c710e8fe","tid":508843,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"孔聖先師<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}